설치: README에는 설명되지 않은 추가 설치 패키지

- Install Boost Libraries:
> sudo apt-get install libboost-all-dev
> export CMAKE_PREFIX_PATH=/usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/cmake/Boost-1.71.0/

- Install automotive-dlt:
> sudo apt-get install libdlt-dev
> export PKG_CONFIG_PATH=/usr/lib/pkgconfig:$PKG_CONFIG_PATH

- Install the systmd development libraries:
> sudo apt-get install libsystemd-dev
> export PKG_CONFIG_PATH=/usr/lib/pkgconfig:$PKG_CONFIG_PATH

- Install Google Benchmark:
> sudo apt-get install libbenchmark-dev
> export CMAKE_PREFIX_PATH=/usr/local/lib/cmake/benchmark:$CMAKE_PREFIX_PATH

- Install Google Test:
> sudo apt-get install libgtest-dev
> export GTEST_ROOT=/usr/src/gtest

위와 같이 모두 설치하고 나서, vsomeip/build 디렉토리에서 cmake .. 명령을 실행시켰는데 GTEST_ROOT is not defined. 에러 메시지가 나옴.

그래서 cmake -DGTEST_ROOT=$GTEST_ROOT .. 와 같이 명령을 실행시켰더니 성공!

그리고 make 혹은 make -j$(nproc) 

그리고 make install

